Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:02.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:03.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:06.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came to my homeland, Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different than Earthland, \Nthe world we come from...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, cats have a \Nhigher status than humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'm more \Nimportant than you, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:17.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, can we get back to the main gist, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Happy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} to you, bub.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:58.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Erza-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:08.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Gray Soluge?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:14.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's the Earthland one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:17.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are our friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the others you \Nturned into a lacrima, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza vs. Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza vs. Erza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You aren't \Ngoing to get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:51.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna whup you good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.82,0:02:52.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Natsu's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:53.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.76,0:02:57.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy should be with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you stand, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:09.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill you in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never guessed it \Nwould be me who stands in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an odd feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:31.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Captain of the Second Magic \NRegiment of the Edolas Royal Army, Erza Knightwalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Fairy Tail Wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:41.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me just what the Earthland me has got...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sylpharion!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:47.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Soaring Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When she changed her armor, \Nher speed increased?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mel Force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:19.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No... She's changing the shape of her weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:22.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The form of her armor has changed again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:36.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic allows you to change the \Nshape of your weapons and armor both?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Edolas me \Ncan only change her weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the form of my lance, my \Nphysical battle abilities can be raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:51.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The fundamentals are different, but the \Nend effect is the same as my The Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:56.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon see the true power of \Nmy magic lance, Ten Commandments!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The lacrima in an open square?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like that part was \Nbasically Erza and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, how did you turn back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:12.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I can really go crazy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing? Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mystogan guy's a shady character,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll believe 'im just \Nfor a bit this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pole of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:37.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more where that came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Only two?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up! Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:38.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:39.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're beatin' it outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done? You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:52.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:52.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I'll explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it you can use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, take one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us the details!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of you were turned into a lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:26.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from my Earthland self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You rescued them splendidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gajeels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Gajeel from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a pretty useful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his face! That's a face \Nthat says "I get things done."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:47.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what do you mean \Nwe were turned into lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means she doesn't give \Na crap about your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All the wizards of Fairy Tail \Nhave been turned into lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They were after your magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the lacrima in the \Nopen square was it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was so \Nbig, it was only you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How hella big is the real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a cut face on that lacrima, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, that means \Nit was a section that was cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:25.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still so much I want to ask, \Nbut what were those strange pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called exballs,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're said to be a medicine that \Nlets you use magic in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:35.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk about the rest \Nafter you take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:36.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Said to be?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got 'em from Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Gajeel is also a Dragon Slayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so Anima didn't work on him either, \Njust like Natsu and Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:54.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't sucked over here, \Nbut remained in Earthland?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Mystogan sent Gajeel here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't he come here himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world Dragon Slayer Magic \Ncan be used for a bunch of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:10.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It can turn our friends turned \Ninto lacrima back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:14.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We know where that lacrima is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:22.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel's running wild in the city right \Nnow searching for that giant lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:28.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take Gajeel to where the lacrima is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel should be able to turn \Neveryone back to normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, Natsu and Wendy should also \Nbe able to, but they wouldn't know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! I'll take Gajeel there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:44.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Are you gonna be okay, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:47.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go find Natsu and Wendy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:52.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them are in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:10.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay? Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu is unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So is Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.13,0:10:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry, Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Natsu! How long are you gonna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up already, you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gray...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we'll get them to take exballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.00,0:10:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Open your damn mouth, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:44.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We got them from Gajeel... Didn't \Nyou get one from Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:50.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, maybe \NI do remember him making me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a medicine that lets \Nyou use magic in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:07.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Next up is Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:23.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gotta stop them, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:40.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:47.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla... Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble... Everyone \Nin the guild will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The extraction is complete, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.75,0:12:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power of dragons \Nis indeed magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:22.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it will be a trivial matter \Nto convert {\i1}that{\i0} into a weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:37.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to destroy Extalia, the Royal Army \Nintends to crash the giant lacrima into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to use everyone \Nat Fairy Tail as a giant bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.60,0:12:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:53.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power of the Exceeds and \Nthe lacrima will explode, and fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And magic power will rain down \Nfor eternity on our kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:18.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In Edolas, they have floating islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you all saw some of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they float \Nusing Extalia's magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:28.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It said in the book that they control \Nthe balance of magic in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And our friends that have been turned \Ninto a lacrima are on one of the islands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:34.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One right next to Extalia, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:45.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, floating above the Royal City \Nwhere we are, is Extalia and the lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:51.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll hit the floating island with \NDragon Slayer Magic to accelerate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and crash it into Extalia. That's \Nwhat the Royal Army is planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:13:59.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:06.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic power of Extalia and Fairy \NTail will collide, explode, and fuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:10.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They said magic power will rain down \Non this country for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they do that, then everyone \Nfrom the guild will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:20.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two Erzas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... How the... Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Battles of the giant monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the end of this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't shut up. You won't calm \Ndown... Man, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Gray we know, from Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of stuff happened and we're \Nhere now. So are Gajeel and Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.21,0:15:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy went to stop the lacrima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you just noticed now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.85,0:15:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:15.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're in a basement, so there's \Nno sunlight on me, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:18.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can barely see myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit a sore spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you guys come here to save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:25.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe too, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just noticed me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.71,0:15:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid me... I should have \Nsaid that first thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:36.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No biggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:42.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you all would come and save us, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:52.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I care, but put \Non some clothes, Gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:54.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Since when have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay, all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll find the king, and stop \Nthem from ramming the lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There are two giant monsters out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:12.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it's okay to leave Erza on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:16.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Erza we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then again, so is her opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:22.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, we'll head to Extalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell them to take shelter \Nbecause the kingdom is going to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're going to stop that attack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:35.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we'll stop it. We'll never \Nlet them do it, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I believe in \NNatsu-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:42.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know what other kinds \Nof weapons the Royal Army has!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:45.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to warn them of \Nthe danger, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's something we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't want to go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to the Exceeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:17:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not about being human, \Nor being an Exceed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.29,0:17:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As fellow living things, \Nthere is something we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.47,0:17:26.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Exceeds are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:42.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be by your side. \NYou don't have to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cat! You're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:04.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead you to where the lacrima is \Nthat all our friends were turned into!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:08.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait... Don't just grab me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you return the people \Nto normal from a lacrima?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:15.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shatter it with Dragon Slayer Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That actually works?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did exactly like Mystogan \Nsaid, so no complainin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:25.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mystogan didn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's big.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:37.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's bigger than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:40.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this guild's a real pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I get home, I'm gonna \Neat my fill of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:01.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the First Magic \NRegiment of the Royal Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Panther Lily.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This lacrima is completely \Ncrucial for this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wings? Don't tell me he's an Exceed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword of the Iron Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:31.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is with that \Nstupidly giant sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:02.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can someone like you defeat {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is this King person?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's the King, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's someplace real important!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And where is a real important place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:20.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell should I know? I just got \Nhere in the castle, and so did you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cell was in a high place, and the \Nmiddle garden is really complex looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:31.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a concentric castle city, except \Nsomething is a little different...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Common knowledge on Earthland isn't going to help \Nunderstand Edolas castle construction here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:41.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying, the \Nplace's architecture sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:49.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wouldn't be surprised if there was \Nlike, an amusement park in the castle somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:56.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There really is an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:10.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... You think the king \Nhere's right in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.48,0:21:16.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at your face, I think \Nyou'd get along just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:36.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:49.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This, like, crazy fun magic power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna disappear from \Nthis world soon, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you people understand how we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to get an infinite \Nsupply of magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.43,0:22:08.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it takes to get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're desperate here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let anyone interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.63,0:23:57.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an amusement park inside the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this all move using magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.23,0:24:05.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But who cares about that right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:10.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's just play to \Nour heart's content, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.51,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've completely forgotten \Nour goal, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.96,0:24:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: It's Life!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:19.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, there's a lot \Nof things you ride here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I'm gonna hurl...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:24.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop getting queasy \Njust from your imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.57,0:24:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
